          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your brain was a weather map, draw the clouds or sun over it now." : {
      "comment" : "A doodling prompt that asks the user to draw a weather map with clouds or a sun.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "당신의 머릿속이 날씨 지도라면, 지금 그 위에 구름이나 해를 그려보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果你的大脑是一张天气图，画出现在上面的云彩或太阳。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your focus was a flashlight beam, draw what it is pointing at." : {
      "comment" : "A doodling prompt that asks the user to draw what a flashlight beam is pointing at.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "집중력이 손전등 빛이라면, 지금 무엇을 비추고 있는지 그려보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果你的注意力是一束手电筒光，画出它正照向什么。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "If your stress was a jar of tangled wires, draw how messy the wires are." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "스트레스가 엉킨 전선이 담긴 병이라면, 전선이 얼마나 복잡한지 그려보세요."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "如果你的压力是一罐缠在一起的电线，画出这些电线有多乱。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Imagine seeing a year of your life in a single glance. Each Joodle carries a special piece of memory. Always private. Always yours." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the feature that allows users to see all their past Joodles in one place.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "ko" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "인생의 1년을 한눈에 본다고 상상해 보세요. 각 Joodle에는 특별한 기억의 조각이 담겨 있습니다. 언제나 비공개. 언제나 당신의 것."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "想象一眼纵览你一整年的生活。每个涂鸦承载着一段特别的记忆。始终私密。始终属于你。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
